      "contentText": "Try Scuba 1 dive &bull; 2.5 to 3 hrs &bull; &#8369;3,000 Have you been yearning to experience scuba diving? Our Try Scuba experience is a gentle introduction led by experienced instructors in an exceptional marine environment. Have you been yearning to experience scuba diving? Our Try Scuba experience is a gentle introduction led by experienced instructors in an exceptional marine environment. What to expect: A short classroom session to learn the basics and discover how to use your dive gear Easy, shore entry Basic safety exercises in shallow water Reef exploration to admire coral and marine life Dauin's marine sanctuaries are teeming with life: colorful coral, tropical fish (clownfish, parrotfish, surgeonfish, butterflyfish, angelfish, and batfish), and both green and hawksbill turtles are frequently seen. Duration 2.5 to 3 hrs Minimum age 8 years old Prerequisites None Certification Recognition card only Price &#8369;3,000 Loved the experience? Continue with us and get discounted additional dives or start your Open Water Diver course&mdash;your Try Scuba dive can count as your first dive! SSI Try Scuba Try scuba experience in Dauin",
