      "title": "Level 1 - Supervised diver to 20m (PE20)",
      "excerpt": "Level 1 is the first diving certification. This complete course gives you the skills and confidence needed to dive to 20 meters, anywhere in the world.",
      "tags": [
        "Courses",
        "FFESSM"
      ],
      "image": "assets/Pictures/Dive pictures/Courses/FFESSM/FFESSM-niveau-1-la-tortue-diving-center-philippines.webp",
      "imageAlt": "FFESSM Level 1 course",
      "contentText": "Level 1 - Supervised diver to 20m (PE20) 3 days &bull; Min age 12 &bull; &#8369;19,500 Level 1 is the first diving certification. This complete course gives you the skills and confidence needed to dive to 20 meters, anywhere in the world. Level 1 is the first diving certification. This complete course gives you the skills and confidence needed to dive to 20 meters, anywhere in the world. FFESSM Level 1 is very similar to SSI Open Water Diver. However, Level 1 does not require a final exam and includes fewer open-water exercises. At La Tortue, we make this training both serious, friendly, and inspiring, in a safe and supportive setting. Each session is designed to match your pace in an ocean-respectful environment. What to expect: Theory: sessions with the instructor and PDF course materials provided 6 sea dives in Dauin's protected marine areas to build skills, work on buoyancy, and enjoy the underwater world safely. Our sites offer ideal training conditions: accessible, shallow reefs, abundant marine life, and moderate currents. Duration 3 days Minimum age 12 Prerequisite Medical certificate of no contraindication to diving (CACI) - able to swim Certification Level 1 - Supervised diver to 20m (PE20), recognized worldwide Price &#8369;19,500 Additional fees licence (55 &euro;) and certification card (20 &euro;) FFESSM Level 1 course",
